data.title: What makes a surname ‘Cornish’?
data.meta_description: [The Surnames of Cornwall is now published. For more see here.] So what exactly comprises a Cornish surname and how is this different from a surname in Cornwall? The old saying tells us that 'By Tre, Pol and Pen, you shall know the Cornishmen'. Actually, you won't. At most, you'll only know about one in…
